---
title: Sun-Dried Tomato Pesto, Chicken Tenders and Spinach Penne with Marinated Mozzarella and Garlic Ciabatta
description: If it ain't broke, don't fix it. The old adage rings true in this classic combination of spinach and sun-dried tomatoes with creamy pasta, chicken tenders, and marinated mozzarella. It's a richly satisfying meal that will bring a touch of freshness to your dinner table!
